title: Benghazi legend Mark Geist presents K9 service dog to combat veteran in N.J.
description: At N.J.'s Barefoot Music Festival, Shadow Warriors Project, founded by Mark Geist, as well as Baden K9 group honored an American combat vet with the gift of a service dog.

title: Postpartum depression among birth moms: How women are breaking the stigma
description: Postpartum depression as experienced by new moms is more common than people think, experts told Fox News Digital — and they offered smart advice for handling it.
